nhc_headline: ...TAMMY TURNING EASTWARD AND EXPECTED TO WEAKEN...
summary:
...TAMMY TURNING EASTWARD AND EXPECTED TO WEAKEN...
 As of 11:00 AM AST Sat Oct 28
 the center of Tammy was located near 33.3, -58.7
 with movement E at 12 mph.
 The minimum central pressure was 995 mb
 with maximum sustained winds of about 50 mph.
